Examples

tf = tempfile()
dir.create(tf)
base <- unzip_merfish_demo(tf)
#> returning path to cached zip
y <- file.path(base, "shapes", "cells")
(s <- readShape(y))
#> class: ShapeFrame
#> count: 2389 
#> data(3): geometry radius cell_id
plot(sf::st_as_sf(data(s)), cex=0.2)
